---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Projects | Chris Fahey"
  description="A guided projects overview showing where to go next for proof of execution, product judgment, and implementation detail."
>
  <main id="main-content" class="route-page">
    <section class="route-shell editorial-reveal">
      <div class="route-shell-accent">
        <p class="route-eyebrow">Projects</p>
        <p class="route-kicker">Proof path</p>
      </div>
      <h1>Proof of execution, organized for quick evaluation.</h1>
      <p class="route-intro route-lede">
        Review the work through delivery context, product judgment, and implementation detail. Each project summary is designed to help evaluators
        decide quickly which proof is worth opening next.
      </p>
      <ul class="route-meta" aria-label="Projects page context">
        <li>Structured to reward quick scanning before deeper reading</li>
        <li>Calm shell treatment that matches the homepage instead of resetting visually</li>
        <li>Built to support credible proof pages as Epic 2 expands the project library</li>
      </ul>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
